Sarrafa kansa kumbon sama jannati
A National Aeronautics da Space Administration ta (NASA ta) sarrafa kansa kumbon sama jannati ga hasken rana tsarin bincike zo da yawa a cikin siffofi da kuma masu girma dabam.
Alhãli kuwa sunã yin tsara don cika daban da kuma takamaiman manufa manufofin, da sana&#39;a rabo da yawa a cikin na kowa.
Kowane kumbon sama jannati kunshi daban-daban kimiyya kayan zaba domin wani manufa, da goyan bayan asali subsystems ga lantarki iko, yanayin da fuskantarwa iko, da kuma ga sarrafa bayanai da kuma sadarwa da duniya.
Lantarki ikon ake bukata ta yi aiki da kumbon sama jannati kida da tsarin.
NASA yana amfani da biyu hasken rana daga iri-iri na photovoltaic Kwayoyin da kananan nukiliya janareto zuwa iko da hasken rana da tsarin manufa.
