The Sun
A tattaunawa da abubuwa a cikin hasken rana tsarin dole ne a fara da Sun.
The Sun dwarfs da sauran gawarwakin, wakiltar kimanin 99,86 bisa dari na duka da taro a hasken rana da tsarin; duk na taurari, watanni, asteroids, comets, turɓaya da gas ƙara har zuwa ne kawai game da 0,14 kashi.
Wannan 0,14 kashi wakiltar abu bar kan daga Sun ta samuwar.
Ɗari da tara Qasa za a buƙaci ka shige fadin Sun ta faifai, da ciki zai iya riƙe a kan 1.3 miliyan Qasa.
A matsayin star, da Sun haifar da makamashi ta hanyar aiwatar da Fusion.
Da yawan zafin jiki a cikin Sun ta core ne miliyan 15 digiri Celsius (27 miliyan darajõji Fahrenheit), da kuma matsa lamba akwai 340 biliyan sau Duniya ta iska matsa lamba a cikin tẽku matakin.
The Sun ta surface zafin jiki na 5.500 digiri Celsius (10,000 darajõji Fahrenheit) alama kusan chilly idan aka kwatanta da ta core-zafin jiki.
A hasken rana core, hydrogen iya fis cikin helium, samar da makamashi.
The Sun kuma samar da karfi Magnetic filin da kõguna na caje barbashi, duka mikawa zuwa yanzu fiye da taurari.
The Sun bayyana wa kasance mai aiki ga 4.6 biliyan shekaru, kuma yana da isasshen man fetur ya ci gaba ba ga wani biyar biliyan shekaru ko haka.
A karshen ta rayuwa, da Sun zai fara fus helium a cikin wa mutum abubuwa, ka fara ƙara sama, kyakkyawan girma haka babban abin da ta cafe Duniya.
Bayan shekaru biliyan matsayin &quot;ja giant,&quot; zai ba zato ba tsammani durkushe a cikin wani &quot;fararen Dwarf&quot; - karshe karshen samfurin wani star kamar namu.
Zai iya ɗaukar tiriliyan shekaru su kwantar kashe gaba daya.
Mutane da yawa kumbon sama jannati sun bincika da ta Sun yanayi, amma ba wanda suka samu wani kusa da surface fiye da kimanin kashi biyu cikin uku na nesa daga duniya ga Sun.
Majagaba 5-11, da jagoran uba Venus Orbiter, Voyagers 1 da 2 da sauran kumbon sama jannati sun duk dauka samfur da hasken rana muhalli.
A Ulysses kumbon sama jannati, kaddamar a kan Oktoba 6, 1990, shi ne hadin gwiwa hasken rana manufa na NASA da kuma Turai Space Agency.
Bayan ta yin amfani da Jupiter ta nauyi canja yanayin da, Ulysses zai tashi a kan Sun ta iyakacin duniya yankuna a lokacin 1994 da 1995, kuma zai yi fadi da kewayon karatu ta yin amfani da tara jirgin kimiyya kida.
Mu ne m cewa Sun ne daidai da yadda shi yake.
Idan sun kasance daban-daban a kusan kowace hanya, rayuwa za kusan lalle ba sun ɓullo da a duniya.
Mercury
Samun na farko kusa dashi ra&#39;ayoyi na Mercury shi ne na farko haƙiƙa na Mariner 10 kumbon sama jannati, kaddamar a kan Nuwamba 3, 1973, daga Kennedy Space Center a Florida.
Bayan tafiya na kusan watanni biyar, wanda kunshe a flyby of Venus, da kumbon sama jannati shige cikin 703 kilomita (437 miles) na hasken rana tsarin ta sadarin duniya a kan Maris 29, 1974.
Har Mariner 10, little aka sani game da Mercury.
Har ma da mafi kyau telescopic ra&#39;ayoyi daga Duniya ya nuna Mercury a matsayin indistinct abu rasa wani surface daki-daki.
Duniya ne don haka kusa da Sun cewa mafi yawa ana rasa a hasken rana tsananin haske.
Lokacin da duniya ne wanda ake iya gani a duniya ta sararin sama bayan faduwar rana ko kuma kafin alfijir, an rufe ta da hazo da kura a cikin yanayi.
Sai kawai radar nesa ba wani ambato na Mercury ta surface yanayi kafin a tafiya na Mariner 10.
Da hotunan Mariner 10 radioed a mayar da Duniya saukar da wani tsoho, dauke da cratered surface, a hankali kama namu Moon.
Da hotuna ma ya nuna babbar cliffs crisscrossing duniya.
Wadannan fili aka halicce a lokacin da Mercury ta ciki sanyaya da kuma shrank, buckling duniya ta ɓawon burodi.
Da cliffs ne a matsayin babban matsayin 3 kilomita (2 mil) kuma idan dai 500 kilomita (310 miles).
Kida a kan Mariner 10 gano cewa Mercury yana da rauni Magnetic filin da wata alama da yanayi - a trillionth da yawa daga duniya a yanayi da kuma hada na shugaba na argon, Neon da helium.
Lokacin da duniyar tamu ta madawwama biyu daukan shi mafi kusa ga Sun, surface yanayin zafi Range daga 467 digiri Celsius (872 digiri Fahrenheit) a kan Mercury ta sunlit gefe zuwa -183 digiri Celsius (-298 darajõji Fahrenheit) a cikin duhu gefe.
Wannan fanni a surface zazzabi - 650 digiri Celsius (1,170 darajõji Fahrenheit) - shi ne mafi girma ga guda jiki a cikin hasken rana tsarin.
Mercury a zahiri bakes da freezes a lokaci guda.
Kwana da dare ne a kan dogon Mercury.
A hade da wani jinkirin juyawa zumunta zuwa taurari (59 Duniya kwanaki) da kuma wani m juyin juya halin a kusa da Sun (88 Duniya kwanaki) yana nufin cewa daya Mercury hasken rana rana daukan 176 Duniya kwanaki ko biyu Mercury shekaru - lokacin yana daukan cikin sadarin duniya don kammala biyu falakinsu a kusa da Sun!
Mercury ya bayyana a yi ɓawon burodi na haske silicate dutsen kamar na Duniya.
Masana kimiyya yi ĩmãni Mercury yana da nauyi baƙin ƙarfe-arziki core yin up dan kadan kasa da rabin da ƙarfi.
Da zai sa Mercury ta core ya fi girma, proportionally, fiye da Moon ta core ko wadanda daga wani daga cikin taurari.
Bayan na farko Mercury gamuwa, Mariner 10 sanya biyu ƙarin flybys - a kan Satumba 21, 1974, da kuma Maris 16, 1975 - kafin iko gas amfani da su Orient da kumbon sama jannati aka ƙãre, da manufa da aka kammala.
Kowane flyby ya faru a wannan gida Mercury lokacin da m rabi na duniya da aka hasken. a sakamakon, kuma har yanzu muna ba su gan daya da rabi na duniya ta surface.
Venus
Rufe da m girgije cover, Venus - mu mafi kusa planetary maƙwabcinsa - shi ne na farko duniya da za a bincika.
A Mariner 2 kumbon sama jannati, kaddamar a kan Agusta 27, 1962, shi ne na farko da fiye da dozin nasara Amurka da kuma Soviet manufa domin nazarin m duniya.
Kamar yadda kumbon sama jannati tashi daga ko orbited Venus, shiga cikin yanayi ko a hankali komai a fili a kan Venus &#39;surface, romantic camfin da kuma baki game da maƙwabcinsa aka aza wa sauran.
A kan Disamba 14, 1962, Mariner 2 shige cikin 34,839 kilomita (21,648 mil) na Venus da zama na farko da kumbon sama jannati to duba wani duniyar tamu. jirgin kayan auna Venus for 42 minutes.
Mariner 5, kaddamar a watan Yuni 1967, ya tashi da yawa kusa da duniya.
Wucewa cikin 4.094 kilomita (2,544 mil) na Venus a karo na biyu American flyby, Mariner 5 ta kida auna duniya ta Magnetic filin, ionosphere, radiation belts da yanayin zafi.
A kan ta hanyar Mercury, Mariner 10 ya tashi daga Venus da daukar kwayar cutar ultraviolet hotuna zuwa Duniya nuna girgije wurare dabam dabam alamu a cikin Venusian yanayi.
A cikin bazara da kuma lokacin rani na 1978, biyu kumbon sama jannati aka kaddamar kara unravel da asirai na Venus.
A kan Disamba 4 na wannan shekara, da jagoran uba Venus Orbiter zama na farko da kumbon sama jannati sanya shi a cikin madawwama biyu a kusa da duniya.
Kwanaki biyar daga baya, da biyar raba aka gyara yin sama da biyu kumbon sama jannati - da jagoran uba Venus Multiprobe - shiga Venusian yanayi a wurare daban-daban sama da duniya.
A hudu kananan, mai zaman kanta yi bincike da kuma babban jiki radioed yanayi data mayar da Duniya a lokacin da zuriya ga surface.
Ko da yake tsara don bincika yanayi, daya daga cikin bincike tsira da tasiri da surface da kuma ci gaba da aika data ga wani sa&#39;a.
Venus kama Duniya a size, jiki abun da ke ciki da kuma yawa fiye da hankali fiye da wani a san duniya.
Duk da haka, kumbon sama jannati sun gano gagarumin bambancin da.
Alal misali, Venus &#39;juyawa (yamma zuwa gabas) ne retrograde (baya) idan aka kwatanta da gabas-da-yamma juya na duniya da kuma mafi yawan sauran taurari.
Kamar 96,5 bisa dari na Venus &#39;yanayi (95 sau da yawa kamar yadda Duniya ta) ne carbon dioxide.
Da babba bijiro da batun kafa na duniya a yanayi ne nitrogen.
Venus &#39;yanayi abubuwa kamar greenhouse, bayar da izni hasken rana radiation ya kai surface amma yi garkuwa da zafin rana da zai Kodayake a radiated baya a sararin samaniya.
A sakamakon haka, duniya ta talakawan surface zafin jiki ne 482 digiri Celsius (900 digiri Fahrenheit), zafi isa ya narke gubar.
A rediyo altimeter a kan jagoran uba Venus Orbiter bayar na farko wajen ganin ta cikin duniyar tamu ta m girgije murfin kuma kayyade surface fasali a kan kusan dukan duniya.
NASA ta Magellan kumbon sama jannati, kaddamar a kan May 5, 1989, ya madawwama biyu a kusa da Venus tun Agusta 10, 1990.
Da kumbon sama jannati yana amfani da radar-zana taswira dabaru don samar da ultrahigh-ƙuduri images na surface.
Magellan Ya saukar da wani wuri mai faɗi mamaye volcanic fasali, zunubanku, kuma tasiri craters.
Babbar yankunan da surface nuna shaidar mahara lokaci na lawa ambaliya da gudana kwance a saman baya su.
An dagagge yankin mai suna Ishtar Terra ne mai lawa-cika tasa kamar yadda manyan kamar yadda Amurka.
A daya karshen wannan tudu zaune Maxwell Montes, wani dutse da girman Dutsen Everest.
Scarring dutsen ta flank ne mai 100-kilomita (62-mile) fadi, 2.5-kilomita (1.5-mil) zurfi tasiri bakin dutse mai suna Cleopatra.
(Kusan duk fasali a kan Venus da ake mai suna ga mata; Maxwell Montes, Alpha Regio da Beta Regio su ne ware.)
Craters tsira a Venus ga watakila 400 shekaru miliyan domin babu ruwa kuma sosai kadan iska yashwa.
M laifi-line cibiyoyin sadarwa rufe duniya, tabbas sakamakon wannan crustal flexing cewa samar farantin tectonics a duniya.
Amma a Venus da surface zafin jiki ya ishe su rasa ƙarfi da dutsen, wanda fasa kawai game ko&#39;ina, hana samuwar manyan faranti da kuma manyan girgizar kasa laifuffuka kamar San Andreas laifi a California.
Venus &#39;m weather juna ne mai high-tsawo, high-gudun wurare dabam dabam na girgije ke dauke da sulfuric acid.
A gudu kai matsayin babban matsayin 360 kilomita (225 miles) a kowace awa, girgije da&#39;irar duniya a kawai hudu Duniya kwanaki.
A wurare dabam dabam da ke cikin wannan shugabanci - yamma zuwa gabas - kamar yadda Venus &#39;jinkirin juyawa na 243 Duniya kwanaki, alhãli kuwa Duniya ta iskõki busa a duka inda - yamma zuwa gabas da gabas zuwa yamma - a shida alternating makada.
