Duniya
Kamar yadda kyan gani, daga sararin samaniya, mu duniya bayãnin hukuncin halaye ne da blue ruwan, ruwan kasa da kuma kore ƙasar talakawa da fari girgije.
Muna wajaba wani teku na iska kunshi 78 cikin dari nitrogen, 21 bisa dari oxygen da kuma 1 cikin dari sauran yayan.
Iyakar abin da duniya, a cikin hasken rana tsarin da aka sani ga riƙe rayuwa, Duniya falakinsu da Sun a wani talakawan nisa na 150 da miliyan kilomita (93 miliyan miles).
Ƙasã, ita ce ta uku duniya daga Sun kuma na biyar mafi girma a cikin hasken rana tsarin, tare da diamita kawai &#39;yan mutum ɗari kilomita fi girma fiye da na Venus.
Mu duniyar tamu ta m juya da zubi nickel-core baƙin ƙarfe ba Yunƙurin zuwa wani m Magnetic filin, wadda, tare da yanayi, garkuwoyi da mu daga kusan duk na cutarwa radiation ya fito daga cikin Sun kuma sauran taurari.
Duniya ta yanayi kare mu daga meteors da, mafi yawan abin da ƙone kafin su iya buge da surface.
Active ma&#39;aunan kasa tafiyar matakai sun bar wata shaida da ya sãmu Duniya kusan lalle samu nan da nan bayan kafa - game da 4.6 biliyan shekaru da suka wuce.
Tare da wasu sabuwar kafa taurari, da aka ¡uraishi da sarari tarkace a farkon zamanin da hasken rana da tsarin.
Daga tafiya a sararin samaniya, muka koya da yawa game da gidanmu duniya.
Na farko American tauraron dan adam - Explorer 1 - aka kaddamar daga Cape Canaveral a Florida a ranar 31 Janairu, 1958, da kuma gano wani tsanani radiation zone, yanzu ake kira da Van Allen radiation belts, kewaye Duniya.
Tun daga nan, wasu bincike da tauraron dan adam sun bayyana cewa mu duniyar tamu ta Magnetic filin da aka gurbata a cikin wani hawaye maniyyi siffar da hasken rana da iska - da rafi caje barbashi ci gaba fita daga Sun.
Mun koyi cewa Magnetic filin ba Fade kashe a sararin samaniya amma yana da tabbataccen iyaka.
Kuma mun san cewa yanzu mu wispy babba yanayi, da zarar ya yi ĩmãni kwantar da hankula da kuma uneventful, seethes da aiki - kumburi da rana da kuma yin kwangila da dare.
Shafi canje-canje a hasken rana aiki, na sama yanayi na taimaka wa yanayi da kuma sauyin yanayi a duniya.
Kuma shafi Duniya ta weather, hasken rana aiki ya ba Yunƙurin zuwa ban mamaki na gani sabon abu a cikin yanayi.
A lokacin da caje barbashi daga hasken rana da iska zama kama a tarko a duniya a Magnetic filin, su yi karo da iska kwayoyin sama mu duniyar tamu ta Magnetic dogayen sanda.
Wadannan iska kwayoyin to fara haske da aka sani da auroras ko arewacin da kuma kudancin hasken wuta.
Tauraron dan adam game 35.789 kilomita (22,238 mil) fita a sarari na taka muhimmiyar rawa a kullum na gida yanayi kiyasin.
Wadannan m lantarki idanu yi gargaɗi mu na kawo hadari hadari.
M duniya saka idanu samar da wani sararin adadin da amfani da bayanai da kuma na taimaka wa mafi fahimtar Duniya ta hadaddun yanayin tsarin.
Daga na musamman vantage maki, da tauraron dan adam na iya nazarin Duniya ta teku, ƙasar amfani da albarkatun, da kuma saka idanu duniya ta kiwon lafiya.
