The Moon
The Moon ne Duniya ta guda halitta tauraron dan adam.
Na farko dan Adam zambiyõyin a kan wani dan hanya duniya da aka yi da &#39;yan saman jannati Amurka a kan m surface na mu airless, m abokin.
A cikin shiri domin mutum-crewed Apollo expeditions, NASA tura da sarrafa kansa Ranger, Surveyor da Lunar Orbiter kumbon sama jannati zuwa nazarin Moon tsakanin 1964 da 1968.
NASA ta Apollo shirin bar babban wasiyya da Lunar kayan da bayanai.
Shida biyu yar sama jannati crews komai a fili a kan da kuma bincika Lunar surface tsakanin 1969 da 1972, dauke da baya tarin duwatsu da ƙasa yin la&#39;akari a total of 382 kilo (842 fam) da kuma kunshi fiye da 2,000 daban samfurori.
Daga wannan abu da kuma sauran karatu, masana kimiyya sun gina wani tarihi na Moon da ya hada da reno ina qarami.
Duwatsu tattara daga Lunar tsaunuka nema wa game da 4.0-4.3 biliyan shekara.
Na farko &#39;yan shekaru miliyan na Moon ta zama kasance haka tashin hankali da&#39; yan burbushi na wannan lokaci kasance.
