Sa&#39;an nan, domin na gaba shekaru miliyan 700 - daga game da 3.8 zuwa 3.1 biliyan shekaru da suka wuce - lawa ya tashi daga cikin Moon.
A lawa hankali shimfiɗa ta a kan surface, ambaliya da manyan tasiri daruna ta samar da duhu yankunan da Galileo Galilei, wani falaki na Italian Renaissance, da ake kira maria, ma&#39;ana tekuna.
