Tun daga nan, Lunar surface na yanzu bata ne kawai ta hanyar micrometeorites, da atomic barbashi daga Sun kuma taurari, da rare tasirin da manyan meteorites kuma da kumbon sama jannati da &#39;yan saman jannati.
Idan mu &#39;yan saman jannati ya sauka a kan Moon a biliyan shekaru da suka wuce, da sun ga wani wuri mai faɗi sosai kama da wanda a yau.
Dubban shekaru, daga yanzu, zambiyõyin bar ta Apollo crews zai zauna kaifi kuma bayyana.
