Mars
Dukan taurari, Mars ya dade da aka gani cikin hasken rana tsarin ta Firayim dan takarar domin da mafaka ga Extraterrestrial rayuwa.
Masana ilmin nazarin ja duniyar tamu ta hanyar nesa ga abin da ya bayyana gare su mike Lines crisscrossing da surface.
Wadannan lura - daga baya m ya zama na gani komai bane illa kawayeniya - kai ga rare ra&#39;ayi cewa hankali wanda yake ya gina wani tsarin na ban ruwa canals a duniya.
A 1938, lokacin da Orson Welles watsa shirye-shirye a rediyo wasan kwaikwayo dangane da almarar kimiyya classic War halittu da HG Wells, isa mutane ĩmãni da labari na invading martians to sa a kusa da tsoro.
Wani dalilin da masana kimiyya ya sa ran rai a duniyar Mars da ya yi tare da bayyana yanayi launi canje-canje a duniya ta surface.
Wannan sabon abu ya kai ga hasashe cewa yanayin zai goyi bayan wani Bloom na martian ciyayi a lokacin warmer watanni da yi wa shuka rayuwa ya zama dormant a lokacin colder lokaci.
Ya zuwa yanzu, shida American manufa domin Mars an za&#39;ayi.
Hudu Mariner kumbon sama jannati - uku Flying ta duniya kuma daya sanya a cikin martian madawwama biyu - surveyed duniya a baje kafin Viking Orbiters da Landers isa.
Mariner 4, kaddamar a marigayi 1964, ya tashi da Mars a kan Yuli 14, 1965, zuwa cikin 9,846 kilomita (6,118 mil) na surface.
Watsin ga Duniya 22 kusa dashi hotuna na duniya, da kumbon sama jannati samu da yawa craters da ta halitta abin da ke faruwa tashoshi amma wata shaida na wucin gadi canals ko sunã gudãna ruwa.
Mariners 6 da 7 bi da flybys a lokacin zafi na 1969 da kuma mayar da 201 hotuna.
Mariners 4, 6 da 7 nuna wani bambancin da surface yanayi da kuma na bakin ciki, sanyi, bushe yanayi na carbon dioxide.
A kan May 30, 1971, da Mariner 9 Orbiter aka kaddamar a kan wani manufa a yi a shekara-dogon nazari na martian surface.
Da kumbon sama jannati isa biyar da rabi watanni bayan-kashe daga, kawai a sami Mars a tsakiyar wata duniyar tamu-fadi da ƙura hadari cewa ya yi surface daukar hoto ba zai yiwu ba ga dama makonni.
Amma bayan da hadari barrantar, Mariner 9 fara dawo na farko na hotunan 7.329. wadannan saukar a baya ba a sani ba martian fasali, ciki har da shaida cewa mai yawa na ruwa sau daya flowed a fadin surface, etching kogin kwari da kuma ambaliyar ruwa filayen.
A watan Agusta da Satumba 1975, da Viking 1 da kumbon sama jannati 2 - kowane kunshi wani orbiter da lander - dauke kashe daga Kennedy Space Center.
