Asteroids
Da hasken rana da tsarin yana da babban yawan m da kuma ƙarfe abubuwa da suke madawwama biyu a kusa da Sun amma sun fi kananan to a yi la&#39;akari cikakken fledged taurari.
Wadannan abubuwa ana da aka sani da asteroids ko qananan taurari.
Mai, amma ba dukan, ana samun a cikin wani band ko bel tsakanin falakinsu na duniyar Mars da Jupiter.
Wasu da falakinsu wanda haye Duniya ta hanya, kuma babu shaidar cewa Duniya da aka buga ta asteroids a baya.
Daya daga cikin kalla eroded, mafi kyau kiyaye su misalai ne Barringer meteor bakin dutse kusa Winslow, Arizona.
Asteroids ne kayan bar kan daga samuwar cikin hasken rana tsarin.
Daya ka&#39;idar da shawara cewa su ne ragowar a duniya da aka hallaka a wani m karo da dadewa.
Mafi kusantar, asteroids ne kayan cewa ba coalesced a cikin wani duniyar tamu.
A gaskiya, idan kiyasta jimlar taro na duk asteroids aka tattara a cikin wani abu guda, da abu zai zama ba fãce game da 1,500 kilomita (932 miles) a fadin - kasa da rabin diamita na mu Moon.
Dubban asteroids da aka gano daga duniya.
An kiyasta cewa 100,000 ne mai haske isa ya ƙarshe za a photographed ta hanyar Duniya na tushen nesa.
Da yawa daga cikin fahimta game da asteroids ya zo daga nazarin guda na sarari tarkace cewa fada da surface na Duniya.
Asteroids cewa kasance a kan karo shakka da Duniya an kira meteoroids.
A lõkacin da wata meteoroid ta sãme mu yanayi a high gudu, gogayya sa wannan bantara na sarari al&#39;amari su incinerate a cikin wani gudana haske da aka sani da wani meteor.
Idan meteoroid ba ya ƙone gaba daya, me ke hagu sãme Duniya ta surface da ake kira a meteorite.
Daya daga cikin mafi kyau wurare nemi meteorites ne kankara hula na Antarctica.
Dukan meteorites yayi nazari, 92,8 cikin dari da ake hada da silicate (dutse), da kuma 5.7 cikin dari da ake hada da baƙin ƙarfe, da nickel. Sauran su ne a cakuda uku kayan.
Stony meteorites su ne mafi wuya su gane tun da sun duba sosai kamar terrestrial duwatsu.
Tun asteroids ne kayan daga sosai a farkon hasken rana tsarin, masana kimiyya da sha&#39;awar a cikin abun da ke ciki.
Kumbon sama jannati cewa sun Flown ta hanyar asteroid bel sun gano cewa, bel shi ne ainihin quite komai da cewa asteroids rabu da manya-manyan nisa.
Yanzu da kuma nan gaba manufa za ta tashi ta zaba asteroids for kusa jarrabawa.
Da Galileo Orbiter, kaddamar da NASA a watan Oktoba 1989, za su gudanar da bincike main-bel asteroids a kan ta hanyar Jupiter.
A tauraro mai wutsiya rendezvous / Asteroid Flyby (CRAF) da kuma Cassini manufa za ta yi nazarin wadannan nisa-jẽfa abubuwa.
Shirya domin jefa a cikin na ƙarshen ɓangare na 1990s, da CRAF da Cassini manufa ne hadin baki aikin na NASA, Turai Space Agency da tarayya sarari hukumomin na Jamus da Italiya, da kuma {asar Amirka, Air Force da sashen Energy .
Wata rana, sarari masana&#39;antu za su gare ni da asteroids ga raw kayan.
Jupiter
Bayan Mars da asteroid bel, a cikin matsanancin yankuna na mu hasken rana tsarin, ƙarya da giant taurari na Jupiter, Rubin, Uranus da Neptune.
A 1972, NASA tura na farko na hudu kumbon sama jannati slated da za su gudanar na farko safiyo wadannan halittu imbin yawa na gas, da watanni da kankara da dutsen.
Jupiter shi ne na farko tashar jiragen ruwa na kira.
Majagaba 10, wanda dauke kashe daga Kennedy Space Center a watan Maris 1972, shi ne ya fara kumbon sama jannati zuwa shiga cikin asteroid bel da kuma tafiya zuwa cikin matsanancin yankuna na hasken rana tsarin.
A watan Disamba 1973, ta mayar da farko kusa dashi images of Jupiter, yawo cikin 132,252 kilomita (82,178 mil) na duniya ta hada girgije fi.
Majagaba 11 bi a shekara daga baya.
Voyagers 1 da 2 da aka kaddamar a lokacin rani na 1977 da kuma mayar da m hotunan da Jupiter da iyali na tauraron dan adam a lokacin flybys a 1979.
Wadannan matafiya samu Jupiter ya zama babban whirling ball na ruwa hydrogen da helium, shugaba tare da m yanayi hada mafi yawa na gaseous hydrogen da helium.
Ammonia kankara lu&#39;ulu&#39;u ne samar da fari Jovian girgije.
Sulfur mahadi (da watakila phosphorus) na iya samar da launin ruwan kasa da kuma orange launukansa cewa faye hali Jupiter ta yanayi.
Shi ne wata ila cewa methane, ammonia, ruwa da sauran gases amsa ta samar da hanyoyin gudanar da kwayoyin a cikin yankuna tsakanin duniyar tamu ta frigid girgije fi da warmer hydrogen teku kwance a kasa.
Saboda Jupiter ta yanayi kuzarin kawo cikas, duk da haka, wadannan kwayoyin mahadi - idan sun wanzu - ne mai yiwuwa short-rayu.
Mai girma Red Spot da aka lura ga ƙarni ta hanyar nesa a duniya.
Wannan guguwa-kamar hadiri a Jupiter ta yanayi ne fiye da sau biyu, girman mu duniyar tamu.
A matsayin high-matsa lamba yankin, Mai girma Red Spot spins a cikin wani shugabanci daura da na low-matsa lamba hadari a Jupiter; an kewaye da swirling igiyoyin cewa juya a kusa da tabo da kuma wani lokaci ana cinye ta da shi.
Mai girma Red Spot zai yi a shekaru miliyan haihuwa.
Mu kumbon sama jannati gano walƙiya a Jupiter ta sama yanayi da kuma lura auroral watsi kama da Duniya ta arewacin hasken wuta a Jovian iyakacin duniya yankuna.
Voyager 1 mayar da farko images of wani suma, ƙunci zobe kewaye Jupiter.
Mafi girma a cikin hasken rana tsarin ta taurari, Jupiter takan juya a wani dizzying taki - sau daya a kowace 9 hours 55 minutes 30 seconds.
A m duniya daukan kusan 12 Duniya da shekara don kammala tafiya a kusa da Sun.
Tare da 16 da aka sani watanni, Jupiter wani abu mai dada hasken rana tsarin.
Wani sabon manufa don Jupiter - da Galileo Project - shi ne a karkashin hanya.
Bayan wani six- shekara cruise cewa daukan da Galileo Orbiter da zarar da Venus, sau biyu da Duniya da Moon kuma ya taba da biyu asteroids, da kumbon sama jannati za su sauke wani yanayi bincike a cikin Jupiter ta girgije yadudduka da kuma isar data mayar da Duniya.
Da Galileo Orbiter zai ciyar shekaru biyu circling duniya da kuma tashi kusa da Jupiter ta manyan watanni, binciko, daki-daki abin da biyu Pioneers da biyu Voyagers saukar.
Bagalile tauraron-dan adam
A 1610, Galileo Galilei da nufin ya kawo nesa kusa a Jupiter da hange hudu da maki haske orbiting duniya.
A karo na farko, mutane sun ga watanni wani duniya.
Don girmama su discoverer, wadannan hudu jikinsu zai zama a san matsayin Bagalile da tauraron dan adam, ko watanni.
Amma Galileo zai yi farin ciki ciniki wannan girmamawa ga wanda look a dazzling hotunan mayar da Voyager kumbon sama jannati kamar yadda suka tashi da wadannan duniya-sized da tauraron dan adam.
Daya daga cikin mafi ƙwarai binciken na Voyager manufa shi ne gaban aiki volcanoes a kan Bagalile moon IO.
Volcanic eruptions bata taba gani a duniya, wanin Duniya.
A Voyager kyamarori gano akalla tara aiki volcanoes a kan IO, tare da plumes na fita kayan mikawa har zuwa 280 kilomita (175 miles) sama da watã ta surface.
IO ta pizza-canza launin ƙasa, alama ta orange da kuma rawaya launukansa, ne mai yiwuwa sakamakon sulfur mai arzikin kayan kawo wa surface da volcanic aiki.
Volcanic aiki a kan wannan tauraron dan adam ne sakamakon tidal flexing sa da gravitational Tug-na-yaƙi tsakanin IO, Jupiter da sauran uku Bagalile watanni.
Europa, kamar guda size kamar yadda mu Moon, shi ne haske Bagalile tauraron dan adam.
Watã ta surface nuna wani hadadden tsararru na streaks, na nuna ɓawon burodi da aka fractured.
Kama a cikin wani gravitational Tug-na-yaki kamar IO, Europa da aka mai tsanani isa ya sa ta ciki kankara zuwa narke - a fili samar da wani ruwa-ruwa teku.
Wannan teku da aka rufe wani ice ɓawon burodi da ya kafa inda ruwa da aka fallasa su sanyi na sarari.
Europa ta core aka yi da dutsen cewa nutse a cikin hedkwatarsu da.
Kamar Europa, da sauran biyu Bagalile watanni - Ganymede da Callisto - su ne halittu na kankara da dutsen.
Ganymede shi ne mafi girma da tauraron dan adam a cikin hasken rana tsarin - ya fi girma fiye da taurari Mercury da Pluto.
Da tauraron dan adam aka hada da game da 50 bisa dari ruwa ko kankara da sauran dutsen.
Ganymede ta surface na da yankunan daban-daban haske, na nuna cewa, a baya, abu oozed daga cikin moon ta ciki da aka ajiye a wurare daban-daban a kan surface.
Callisto, kawai dan kadan karami fiye da Ganymede, yana da mafi ƙasƙanci yawa daga wani Bagalile tauraron dan adam, bayar da shawara cewa mai yawa na ruwa wani bangare ne na abun da ke ciki.
Callisto shi ne ya fi nauyi cratered abu a cikin hasken rana tsarin. babu aiki a lokacin da tarihi ya ma share tsohon craters fãce mafi tasirin.
Cikakken karatu na dukan Bagalile tauraron dan adam za a yi da Galileo Orbiter.
Rubin
Babu duniya a cikin hasken rana tsarin da aka ƙawãta kamar Rubin.
Its dadi zobe tsarin shi ne unrivaled.
Kamar Jupiter, Rubin aka hada mafi yawa na hydrogen.
Amma da bambanci da m launuka da daji haukan kogi samu a Jovian girgije, Rubin ta yanayi yana da mafi dabara, butterscotch ya dafa, da markings ake muted ta high-tsawo hazo.
Da aka ba Rubin ta da ɗan placid-neman bayyanar, masana kimiyya suna mamaki a high-gudu Equatorial jet rafi cewa naushe wasu 1.770 kilomita (1,100 mil) awa daya.
Uku American kumbon sama jannati sun ziyarci Rubin.
Majagaba 11 sped ta duniya da watã Titan a watan Satumba 1979, ya dawo na farko kusa dashi images.
Voyager 1 bi a watan Nuwamba 1980, aika da baya gaske hotunan da wahayi a karon farko cikin complexities daga Rubin ta zobe tsarin da watanni.
Voyager 2 tashi da duniya da watanni a watan Agusta 1981.
Da zobba da ake hada da m low-yawa barbashi orbiting akayi daban-daban a kusa da Rubin ta ekweita a m nisa daga girgije fi.
Bincike na kumbon sama jannati rediyo tãguwar ruwa wucewa ta cikin zobba ya nuna cewa da barbashi bambanta yadu a cikin size, jere daga turbaya zuwa gidan-sized boulders.
Da zobba ne mai haske domin lalle ne su mafi yawa kankara da frosted dutsen.
Da zobba iya sa a lõkacin da wata moon ko wani wucewa jiki ventured ma kusa da Rubin.
A m abu da an tsage baya da girma tidal sojojin a kan bãyan tẽkun, kuma a ciki.
Ko da abu mai yiwuwa ba a cika kafa don fara da kuma rududdugaggu a ƙarƙashin rinjayar Rubin ta nauyi.
A na uku yiwuwar shi ne, abu aka rafke da collisions da ya fi girma abubuwa orbiting duniya.
Kasa ko dai ta samar da cikin wani moon ko don shiga wani hali daga juna, mutum zobe barbashi bayyana da za a gudanar a wurin da gravitational Pull na Rubin da tauraron dan adam.
Wadannan hadaddun gravitational interactions samar da dubban ringlets cewa yin sama da manyan zobba.
Radio watsi quite kama da a tsaye ji a kan AM mota rediyo a lokacin wani lantarki hadari aka gano da Voyager kumbon sama jannati.
Wadannan watsi ne na hali na walƙiya amma an yi ĩmãni da za a fito daga Rubin ta zobe tsarin maimakon ta yanayi, inda babu walƙiya aka kiyaye.
Kamar yadda suke yi a Jupiter, da Voyagers ga wata ce ta Duniya ta auroras kusa Rubin ta dogayen sanda.
A Voyagers gano amaryar wata, suka sami dama da tauraron dan adam cewa raba guda madawwama biyu.
Mun koyi cewa wasu watanni kiwon zobe barbashi, rike Rubin ta zobba da kuma gibba, a cikin zobba.
Rubin ta 18th moon aka gano a 1990 daga images dauka Voyager 2 a 1981.
Voyager 1 ƙaddara cewa Titan yana da nitrogen na tushen yanayi da methane da argon - wata kamar Duniya ta a abun da ke ciki fiye da carbon dioxide atmospheres na duniyar Mars da Venus.
Titan ta surface zafin jiki na -179 digiri Celsius (-290 darajõji Fahrenheit) ya nuna cewa akwai zai yi ruwa-kankara tsibirin tanã fita a bisa teku na ethane-methane ruwa ko sludge.
Abin baƙin ciki, Voyager ta kyamarori ba zai iya shiga cikin wata ta m girgije.
Ci gaba da photochemistry daga hasken rana radiation iya tana mayar Titan ta methane ya ethane, acetylene da - a hade tare da nitrogen - hydrogen cyanide.
A karshen fili ne mai gini block na amino acid.
Wadannan yanayi na iya zama kama da na yanayi yanayin primeval Duniya tsakanin uku da hudu biliyan suka wuce.
Duk da haka, Titan ta yanayi da yawan zafin jiki da suka zama ma low zuwa yarda ci gaba bayan wannan mataki kwayoyin sunadarai.
Da bincike na Rubin za ta ci gaba da Cassini manufa.
A Cassini kumbon sama jannati za su kewayewa da duniya da kuma za ta tura wani bincike da ake kira Huygens, wanda za a kika aika a cikin Titan ta yanayi da kuma fada da surface.
Cassini zai yi amfani da bincike da kuma radar to sa&#39;a ta hanyar Titan ta girgije, kuma zai ciyar da shekaru nazarin Saturnian tsarin.
Uranus
A watan Janairu 1986, hudu da rabi bayan shekara ziyartar Rubin, Voyager 2 kammala na farko kusa dashi binciken na Uranian tsarin.
A takaice dai flyby saukar ƙarin bayani game da Uranus da retinue na garin kankara watanni fiye da aka gleaned daga ƙasa lura tun lokacin da duniya ta samu a kan biyu ƙarni da suka wuce da Turanci falakin William Herschel.
Uranus, uku mafi girma daga cikin taurari, na da oddball na hasken rana tsarin.
Ba kamar sauran taurari (amma ban da Pluto), wannan giant ainihin tipped a kan ta gefe tare da arewa da kuma kudu dogayen sanda alternately ta da rana a lokacin wani 84-shekara lilo a kusa da hasken rana da tsarin.
A lokacin Voyager 2 ta flyby, kudu iyakacin duniya fuskanci cikin Sun.
Uranus yiwuwa an buga kan lokacin da wani Duniya-sized abu karo da shi da wuri a cikin rãyuwar da hasken rana da tsarin.
Voyager 2 gano cewa Uranus &#39;Magnetic filin ba ya bi saba arewa maso kudu axis samu a sauran duniyoyi.
A maimakon haka, cikin filin da aka tilted 60 darajõji, kuma biya diyya daga duniyar tamu ta tsakiya, a sabon abu da a duniya zai zama kamar da ciwon daya Magnetic iyakacin duniya a New York City da kuma sauran a birnin Djakarta, a tsibirin Java a Indonesia.
Uranus &#39;yanayi kunshi, yafi na hydrogen, tare da wasu 12 bisa dari helium da adadi kaɗan na ammonia, methane da ruwa tururi.
Duniya ta blue launi na faruwa a saboda methane a cikin yanayi garwaya da dukan sauran launuka.
Iska gudu Range har zuwa 580 kilomita (360 miles) a kowace awa, kuma yanayin zafi a kusa da girgije fi talakawan -221 digiri Celsius (-366 darajõji Fahrenheit).
Uranus &#39;sunlit kudu iyakacin duniya ne tana tattare a cikin wani irin photochemical &quot;smog&quot; yi ĩmãni ya zama mai hade da acetylene, ethane da sauran hasken rana-generated sunadarai.
Kewaye duniya ta yanayi da kuma mikawa dubban kilomita a sararin samaniya ne mai wuyar ganewa ultraviolet Sheen da aka sani da &quot;electroglow.&quot;
Kimanin 8,000 kilomita (5,000 mil) a kasa Uranus &#39;girgije fi, akwai tsammani ya zama babban ruwan teku na ruwa da kuma narkar da ammonia wasu 10,000 kilomita (6,200 mil) zurfi.
Ƙarƙashin wannan teku ne mai Duniya-sized ainihin wa mutum kayan.
Voyager 2 gano 10 amaryar wata, 16-169 kilomita (10-105 mil) a diamita, orbiting Uranus.
Da biyar a baya aka fi sani - Miranda, Ariel, Umbriel, Titania da Oberon - range a size daga 520 zuwa 1.610 kilomita (323 zuwa 1,000 mil) a fadin.
Wakiltar wani ma&#39;aunan kasa yi nuni, wadannan biyar watanni ne rabin kankara, rabin dutsen duniyoyin da suke da sanyi da duhu da kuma nuna shaidar da aiki, ciki har da faulting da kankara gudana.
Mafi na ƙwarai daga Uranus &#39;watanni ne Miranda.
Its surface siffofi babban cliffs da canyons, bakin dutse-pocked filayen kwaruruka, da Winding.
A kaifi saɓani a cikin ƙasa bayar da shawarar cewa, bayan da wata kafa, aka fasa baya da wani karo da wani jiki - wani taron ba sabon abu a cikin hasken rana tsarin, wanda ya ƙunshi mutane da yawa abubuwa da cewa suna da tasiri craters ko ne, niƙaƙƙun gaɓãɓuwa ​​daga manyan tasirin.
Mene ne m shi ne, Miranda a fili sauya tare da wasu daga cikin kayan da suka kasance a ciki fallasa a kan bãyan tẽkun.
Uranus aka yi tsammani a yi tara duhu zobba. Voyager 2 imaged 11.
Ya bambanta da Rubin ta zobba, wanda aka hada da haske barbashi, Uranus &#39;zobba da ake da farko ya tashi daga duhu, dutse-sized chunks.
Neptune
Voyager 2 kammala ta 12-shekara yawon shakatawa na hasken rana da tsarin da wani bincike na Neptune da duniya ta watanni.
A kan Agusta 25, 1989, da kumbon sama jannati share su cikin 4,850 kilomita (3,010 mil) na Neptune, sa&#39;an nan ya tashi a kan yi ga watã Triton.
A lokacin Neptune gamuwa da shi ya bayyana cewa duniya ta yanayi ya fi aiki fiye da Uranus &#39;.
Voyager 2 lura Mai girma Dark Spot, a madauwari hadari girman Duniya, a Neptune ta yanayi.
Kama Jupiter ta Great Red Spot, da hadari spins counterclockwise da kuma motsa yamma a kusan 1,200 kilomita (745 miles) awa daya.
Voyager 2 kuma lura da karami duhu tabo da azumi-motsi girgije An Kwafa da &quot;babur,&quot; da kuma high-tsawo girgije a kan babban hydrogen da helium girgije bene.
A mafi iska gudu na kowane duniya aka lura, har zuwa 2,400 kilomita (1,500 mil) awa daya.
Kamar sauran giant taurari, Neptune yana da gaseous hydrogen da helium babba Layer a kan wani ruwa ciki.
Duniya ta core ƙunshi mafi girma yawan dutsen da karfe fiye da wadanda na sauran gas Refayawa.
Neptune ta rarrabe blue bayyanar, kamar Uranus &#39;blue launi, shi ne saboda yanayi methane.
Neptune ta Magnetic filin da aka tilted zumunta zuwa duniya ta juya axis da ba a tsakiya a core.
Wannan sabon abu ne kama da Uranus &#39;Magnetic filin da shawara cewa saura na biyu Kattai ana generated a cikin wani wuri sama da tsakiya, inda matsa lamba ne don haka mai girma cewa ruwa hydrogen kwakwalwa gaba da lantarki Properties na wani karfe.
Duniya ta Magnetic filin, a daya bangaren, an samar da da kadi ƙarfe core da aka sani kawai dan kadan tilted da biya diyya zumunta a cikin hedkwatarsu da.
Voyager 2 kuma zubar da haske a kan asiri na Neptune ta zobba.
Abun Lura daga Duniya ya nuna cewa akwai arcs of kayan madawwama biyu a kusa da giant duniya.
Ba bayyana yadda Neptune zai iya samun arcs da kuma yadda wadannan za a iya kiyaye daga yada fita zuwa ko da, unclumped zobba.
Voyager 2 gano wadannan arcs, amma sun kasance, a gaskiya, kashi na bakin ciki, gama zobba.
A yawan kananan watanni iya bayyana arcs, amma irin wannan jikin ba hange.
Masana ilmin ya gano Neptunian watanni Triton a 1846 da kuma Nereid a 1949.
Voyager 2 sami shida more.
Daya daga cikin amaryar wata - Proteus - shi ne ainihin ya fi girma fiye Nereid, amma tun Proteus falakinsu kusa da Neptune, da aka rasa a cikin duniyar tamu ta tsananin haske ga masu lura a duniya.
Triton da&#39;ira Neptune a cikin wani retrograde madawwama biyu a karkashin kwanaki shida.
Tidal sojojin a kan Triton aka haddasa shi a karkace sannu a hankali zuwa ga duniya.
A 10 zuwa 100 shekaru miliyan (wani ɗan gajeren lokaci a astronomical sharuddan), da watã za ta kasance ta kusa da Neptunian nauyi zai tsaga shi baya, forming wani m zobe zuwa bi duniya ta suna fadin halin yanzu zobba.
Triton ta wuri mai faɗi kamar m da m kamar yadda waɗanda suke na IO da Miranda.
Watã yana da mafi dutsen fiye da takwarorinsu a Rubin da Uranus.
Triton ta alkyabbar ne mai yiwuwa hada da ruwa-kankara, amma watã ta ɓawon burodi ne mai bakin ciki veneer da nitrogen da methane.
Watã ya nuna biyu da cika fuska daban-daban na ƙasa: abin da ake kira &quot;cantaloupe&quot; ƙasa da matafã ba kankara hula.
Dark streaks bayyana a kan kankara hula.
Wadannan streaks su ne fallout daga geyser-kamar volcanic vents cewa harba nitrogen gas da kuma duhu, m-grained barbashi don Heights na 2 zuwa 8 kilomita (1 zuwa 5 mil).
Triton ta bakin ciki yanayi, amma 1 / 70,000th kamar yadda m kamar yadda Duniya ta, yana da iskõki cewa kawo cikin duhu barbashi da saka su a matsayin streaks a kan kankara hula - da coldest surface duk da haka samu a cikin hasken rana tsarin (-235 digiri Celsius, -391 darajõji Fahrenheit).
Triton zai yi kamar Pluto ya fi kowane abu kumbon sama jannati sun zuwa yanzu ziyarci.
Pluto
Pluto shi ne ya fi nisa daga cikin taurari, duk da haka eccentricity na madawwama biyu lokaci-lokaci daukawa shi a ciki Neptune ta madawwama biyu, inda ya kasance tun 1979 ya kuma inda zai zauna har Maris 1999.
Pluto ta madawwama biyu kuma sosai karkata - tilted 17 darajõji ga orbital jirgin sama na sauran taurari.
Gano a 1930, Pluto bayyana su zama kadan fiye da a wani sarari suKe snowball.
Duniya ta diamita an lasafta su zama kamar 2,300 kilomita (1,430 mil), kawai kashi biyu cikin uku na girman mu Moon.
Ground na tushen lura nuna cewa Pluto ta surface aka rufe methane kankara da cewa akwai wani bakin ciki yanayi da zai daskare da fada wa surface kamar yadda duniya motsa daga Sun.
Abun Lura nuna cewa Pluto ta juya axis ne tipped da 122 digiri.
Duniya yana daya a san da tauraron dan adam, Charon, gano a 1978.
Charon ta surface abun da ke ciki ya bambanta Pluto ta: watã ya bayyana da za a rufe da ruwa-kankara maimakon methane kankara.
Its madawwama biyu ne gravitationally kulle tare da Pluto, don haka duka gawawwakin ko da yaushe kiyaye guda rabin ƙwalo suna fuskantar juna.
Pluto ta da Charon ta rotational lokacin da Charon ta tsawon juyin juya halin duka 6.4 Duniya kwanaki.
Ko da yake ba kumbon sama jannati sun taba kai ziyara Pluto, NASA a halin yanzu binciko da yiwuwar irin wannan manufa.
Comets
A outermost mambobi ne na hasken rana da tsarin lokaci-lokaci biya ziyara a ciki taurari.
Kamar yadda asteroids su ne m da kuma ƙarfe remnants na da samuwar cikin hasken rana tsarin, comets ne garin kankara tarkace daga wannan rage farkon da zai iya tsira ne kawai da nisa daga Sun.
Mai tauraro mai wutsiya nuclei kasance a cikin Oort Cloud, a sako-sako da taro na abubuwa a cikin wani Halo bayan da taurari da kuma kai watakila halfway to mafi kusa star.
Tauraro mai wutsiya nuclei madawwama biyu a cikin wannan daskararre abyss har an gravitationally perturbed cikin sabon falakinsu wanda ɗauke su kusa da Sun.
A matsayin tsakiya da dama a cikin falakinsu na cikin matsanancin taurari, da maras tabbas abubuwa na abin da aka yi hankali dumi. da lokacin da tsakiya shiga yankin na ciki taurari, wadannan maras tabbas abubuwa da ake ruwan.
A tsakiya kanta ne wanda bai bi ka&#39;ida ko doka ba da kuma kawai &#39;yan mil fadin, kuma an sanya principally na ruwa-kankara da methane da ammonia - kayan sosai kama da wadanda composing da watanni na giant taurari.
Kamar yadda wadannan kayan tafasa a kashe na tsakiya, da suka samar da wata coma ko girgije-kamar &quot;kai&quot; da za a iya auna dubban kilomita fadin.
Da coma tsiro a matsayin tauraro mai wutsiya samun kusa da Sun.
A rafi caje barbashi ya fito daga cikin Sun Firaministan a kan wannan girgije, hurawa shi da baya kamar flag a cikin iska, ba Yunƙurin zuwa ga tauraro mai wutsiya ta &quot;wutsiyoyi.&quot;
Gas kuma ions aka nike kai tsaye da baya daga tsakiya, amma kura barbashi an tura karin sannu a hankali.
Kamar yadda tsakiya ya ci gaba a cikin madawwama biyu, da ƙura barbashi an bari a baya a cikin wani mai lankwasa baka.
Biyu da gas da kura wutsiyoyi nuna daga Sun; a sakamako, da tauraro mai wutsiya farauta da wutsiyoyi kamar yadda recedes daga Sun.
A wutsiyoyi iya kai miliyan 150 kilomita (93 miliyan miles) a tsawon, amma jimlar adadin kayan kunshe ne a cikin wannan ban mamaki nuni zai shige a cikin wani akwati talakawa.
Comets - daga Latin cometa, ma&#39;ana &quot;dogon masu gashi&quot; - su ne da gaske ban mamaki haske nuna.
Wasu comets wuce ta cikin hasken rana tsarin sau ɗaya kawai, amma wasu suna da falakinsu gravitationally modified da wani kusa gamuwa da daya daga cikin giant m taurari.
Wadannan karshen baƙi iya shigar da rufaffiyar elliptical falakinsu da akai-akai koma ciki hasken rana tsarin.
Halley ta tauraro mai wutsiya shi ne ya fi shahara misali da wani in mun gwada da kankanen tauraro mai wutsiya, ya dawo a kan talakawan da sau daya a kowace shekara 76 da orbiting daga bayan Neptune zuwa cikin Venus &#39;madawwama biyu.
Tabbatar sightings na tauraro mai wutsiya koma 240 BC Wannan na yau da kullum baƙo zuwa ga hasken rana tsarin ne mai suna for Sir Edmond Halley, saboda ya yi mãkirci ga tauraro mai wutsiya ta madawwama biyu, kuma annabta da take, bisa farkon sightings da Newtonian dokokin motsi.
Sunansa ya zama wani ɓangare na astronomical Lore lokacin, a 1759, da tauraro mai wutsiya koma a kan jadawalin.
Abin baƙin ciki, Sir Edmond ba su zauna su gan shi.
A tauraro mai wutsiya iya zama sosai shahararren a cikin sama, idan ta wuce comparatively kusa da duniya.
Abin baƙin ciki, a ranar da mafi yawan &#39;yan bayyanar, Halley ta tauraro mai wutsiya wuce ba kusa fiye da miliyan 62,4 kilomita (38.8 miliyan miles) daga duniya.
A tauraro mai wutsiya iya ganinsa da tsirara ido, musamman ga masu kallo a kudancin rabin ƙwalo, amma ba m.
Comets kasance haka mai haske, a rare lokatai, abin da suka kasance bayyane a lokacin rana.
Tarihi, tauraro mai wutsiya sightings da aka fassara a matsayin sharri bata bayan shiriya da aka artistically fassara a matsayin rike da wuka a cikin sama.
A tauraro mai wutsiya rendezvous / Asteroid Flyby (CRAF) kumbon sama jannati za ta zama na farko matafiyi ya tashi kusa da wani tauraro mai wutsiya tsakiya da kuma zama a kusanci zuwa gare shi kamar yadda suka kusanci Sun.
CRAF zai tsayar da tsakiya kamar yadda shi ya zama aiki a cikin girma da hasken rana da kuma fara da ta m abubuwa tafasa kashe da kuma samar da wata coma da wutsiyoyi.
Da dama kumbon sama jannati sun Flown ta comets a high gudun; na farko shi ne NASA ta kasa da kasa Cometary Explorer a shekarar 1985.
An armada na biyar kumbon sama jannati (biyu Japan, biyu Soviet da kuma Giotto kumbon sama jannati daga Turai Space Agency) ya tashi daga Halley ta tauraro mai wutsiya a 1986.
Kammalawa
Duk da kokarin sa&#39;a a fadin sararin nisa na sararin samaniya ta hanyar labulen yanayi, masana kimiyya da suka gabata yana daya jiki suke karãtun su a hankali - Duniya.
Amma tun 1959, spaceflight ta cikin hasken rana tsarin ya dauke da shãmaki a kan makwabta a sarari.
Muka koya game da mu hasken rana tsarin da &#39;yan fiye da kowa da a baya dubban shekaru.
Mu sarrafa kansa kumbon sama jannati sun yi tafiya zuwa Moon da kuma duk taurari bayan mu duniya fãce Pluto. da suka lura watanni a matsayin babban matsayin kananan taurari, Flown ta comets da dauka samfur da hasken rana muhalli.
Ilmin taurari littattafai yanzu sun hada da cikakken hotunan gawarwakin da suke kawai smudges a cikin mafi girma nesa ga al&#39;ummomi.
Mu ne m ya zama da rai a yanzu zuwa ga waɗannan m da kyau wurare da abubuwa.
Da ilmi tsiwirwirinsu daga tafiya a cikin hasken rana tsarin ya redefined gargajiya Duniya kimiyyar kamar ilmin duwatsu da kuma meteorology da kawo yaɗuwar nuna kangara mai gaba ɗaya sabon horo kira kamanta planetology.
By nazarin ilmin duwatsu na taurari, watanni, asteroids da comets, da kuma gwada bambance-bambance da kamance, muke koyo game da asalin da tarihin wadannan gawawwaki da hasken rana tsarin a matsayin dukan.
Muna kuma samun m cikin duniya a hadaddun yanayin tsarin.
By ganin yadda yanayin da ake dimbin yawa a kan sauran halittu da ta gudanar da bincike da ta Sun aiki da tasiri a ko&#39;ina cikin hasken rana tsarin, zamu iya fahimtar yanayin damina da kuma tafiyar matakai a duniya.
Za mu ci gaba da koyi da amfana a matsayin mu na sarrafa kansa kumbon sama jannati gano mu unguwa a sarari.
Daya halin yanzu manufa ne zana taswira Venus. wasu suna yawo a tsakanin halittu kuma zai isa Sun kuma Jupiter bayan hadaddun yanayin sabawa.
Nan gaba manufa aka shirya don Mars, Rubin, a tauraro mai wutsiya da asteroid bel.
Mu kuma iya sa ido lokacin da mutane za su sake kafa kafar a kan wani dan hanya duniya.
Ko da yake &#39;yan saman jannati ba su kasance mayar da shi cikin Moon tun Disamba 1972, da tsare-tsaren da ake tsara don mu koma Lunar wuri mai faɗi da kuma ga mutum bincike na Mars har ma da kafa martian outposts.
Wata rana, shan wani biki na iya nufin jawabin a mako, a wata Lunar tushe ko wani martian mallaka!
